<https://w3id.org/rdip> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Ontology> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#versionIRI> <https://w3id.org/rdip/2.0.0/> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#imports> <http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#imports> <http://purl.org/spar/cito/> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#imports> <http://vivoweb.org/ontology/core> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#imports> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#imports> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov-o#> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip> <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/description> "A project-centric ontology for representing the full research lifecycle, provenance chains, agent attribution, software environments, hyperparameters, and contextual links between activities, software, datasets and publications. Version 2 adds qualified PROV-O patterns, dataset derivation chains, activity sequencing, evaluation results, software dependency graphs, and reproducibility-critical metadata."@en .
<https://w3id.org/rdip> <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/title> "RDIP: Research Data Intelligence Platform Ontology"@en .
<https://w3id.org/rdip> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/license> <https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip> <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/preferredNamespacePrefix> "rdip" .
<https://w3id.org/rdip> <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/preferredNamespaceUri> "https://w3id.org/rdip/" .
<https://w3id.org/rdip> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "v2.0: added qualified PROV-O associations, wasDerivedFrom chain, activity sequencing (wasInformedBy), EvaluationResult, SoftwareDependency, EnvironmentSpec, RandomSeed, fixed hasParticipant subPropertyOf, fixed landingPage range conflict, removed duplicate class declarations." .
<https://w3id.org/rdip> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#priorVersion> <https://w3id.org/rdip/1.0.0/> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#versionInfo> "2.0.0" .
