# https://w3id.org/rdip/citesDataset
<https://w3id.org/rdip/citesDataset> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/citesDataset> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://purl.org/spar/cito/citesAsDataSource> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/citesDataset> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/Document> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/citesDataset> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/citesDataset> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Asserts that a publication cites a particular dataset as a data source. Subproperty of cito:citesAsDataSource."@en .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/citesDataset> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "cites dataset"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/rdip/dataFormat
<https://w3id.org/rdip/dataFormat> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/dataFormat> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/format> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/dataFormat> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset> .
# 
