<https://w3id.org/rdip/dependencyName> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/dependencyName> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://schema.org/name> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/dependencyName> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/rdip/SoftwareDependency> .
# 
# https://w3id.org/rdip/derivedFrom
<https://w3id.org/rdip/derivedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/derivedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasDerivedFrom> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/derivedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/derivedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/derivedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Direct dataset-level derivation link. Subproperty of prov:wasDerivedFrom. Use this to close the provenance chain between an input dataset and the dataset produced by a DataProcessingActivity or DataAnalysisActivity. Without this link, PROV-O reasoners cannot infer the artifact-to-artifact lineage."@en .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/derivedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "derived from"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/rdip/executedIn
<https://w3id.org/rdip/executedIn> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/executedIn> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/rdip/ResearchActivity> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/executedIn> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/rdip/ComputingEnvironment> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/executedIn> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a computational ResearchActivity to the ComputingEnvironment in which it was executed. Essential for computational reproducibility."@en .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/executedIn> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "executed in"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/rdip/follows
<https://w3id.org/rdip/follows> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/follows> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/rdip/ResearchActivity> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/follows> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/rdip/ResearchActivity> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/follows> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Inverse of rdip:precedes. An activity that directly follows another in the workflow."@en .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/follows> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "follows"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/rdip/generatesDataset
<https://w3id.org/rdip/generatesDataset> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/generatesDataset> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#generated> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/generatesDataset> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/rdip/ResearchActivity> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/generatesDataset> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/generatesDataset> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Records that a ResearchActivity produced a dcat:Dataset as output. Subproperty of prov:generated."@en .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/generatesDataset> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "generates dataset"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/rdip/generatesPublication
<https://w3id.org/rdip/generatesPublication> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/generatesPublication> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#generated> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/generatesPublication> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/rdip/PublicationActivity> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/generatesPublication> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/Document> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/generatesPublication> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a PublicationActivity to the bibo:Document it produces."@en .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/generatesPublication> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "generates publication"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/rdip/generatesResult
<https://w3id.org/rdip/generatesResult> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/generatesResult> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#generated> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/generatesResult> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/rdip/DataAnalysisActivity> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/generatesResult> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/rdip/EvaluationResult> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/generatesResult> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a DataAnalysisActivity to an EvaluationResult it produces (e.g. a test-set accuracy, F1 score, RMSE). Essential for verifying reproduction: a reproducer compares their re-run results against these stored values."@en .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/generatesResult> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "generates result"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/rdip/generatesSoftware
<https://w3id.org/rdip/generatesSoftware> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/generatesSoftware> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#generated> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/generatesSoftware> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/rdip/SoftwareDevelopmentActivity> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/generatesSoftware> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/rdip/SoftwareApplication> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/generatesSoftware> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a SoftwareDevelopmentActivity to the SoftwareApplication it produces."@en .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/generatesSoftware> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "generates software"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/rdip/hasActivity
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasActivity> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasActivity> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://w3id.org/rdip/isPartOfProject> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasActivity> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/rdip/ResearchProject> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasActivity> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/rdip/ResearchActivity> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasActivity> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a ResearchProject to one of its constituent ResearchActivity instances."@en .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasActivity> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has activity"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/rdip/hasActivityRole
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasActivityRole> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasActivityRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/rdip/ResearchActivity> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasActivityRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/rdip/RoleInActivity> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasActivityRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Simple (unqualified) link from an activity to a RoleInActivity node. For full PROV-O qualified attribution use prov:qualifiedAssociation → rdip:ActivityAssociation instead."@en .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasActivityRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has activity role"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/rdip/hasEnvironmentSpec
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasEnvironmentSpec> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasEnvironmentSpec> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/rdip/ComputingEnvironment> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasEnvironmentSpec> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/rdip/EnvironmentSpec> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasEnvironmentSpec> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a ComputingEnvironment to a machine-actionable EnvironmentSpec (Docker image digest, conda YAML, Nix flake, etc.) that fully describes how to recreate the environment."@en .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasEnvironmentSpec> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has environment specification"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/rdip/hasLeadOrganization
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasLeadOrganization> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasLeadOrganization> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasAssociatedWith> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasLeadOrganization> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://schema.org/sponsor> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasLeadOrganization> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/rdip/ResearchProject> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasLeadOrganization> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://vivoweb.org/ontology/core#Organization> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasLeadOrganization> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a ResearchProject to the Organisation that leads or funds it."@en .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasLeadOrganization> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has lead organization"@en .
