<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasOutput> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/rdip/ResearchProject> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasOutput> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Entity> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasOutput> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a ResearchProject directly to a top-level output entity (dataset, software, publication). For activity-level generation use rdip:generatesDataset / rdip:generatesSoftware / rdip:generatesPublication."@en .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasOutput> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has output"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/rdip/hasParameter
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasParameter> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasParameter> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/rdip/ResearchActivity> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasParameter> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/rdip/Parameter> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasParameter> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a ResearchActivity to a Parameter (hyperparameter, config value, or random seed). Use rdip:RandomSeed for random seeds specifically."@en .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasParameter> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has parameter"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/rdip/hasParticipant
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasParticipant> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasParticipant> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasAssociatedWith> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasParticipant> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://schema.org/contributor> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasParticipant> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/rdip/ResearchProject> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/hasParticipant> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://vivoweb.org/ontology/core#Person> .
