# 
# https://w3id.org/rdip/isPartOfProject
<https://w3id.org/rdip/isPartOfProject> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/isPartOfProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/rdip/ResearchActivity> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/isPartOfProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/rdip/ResearchProject> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/isPartOfProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Inverse of rdip:hasActivity. Asserts that a ResearchActivity belongs to a given ResearchProject."@en .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/isPartOfProject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is part of project"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/rdip/isVersionOf
<https://w3id.org/rdip/isVersionOf> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/isVersionOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/isVersionOf> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/isVersionOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasRevisionOf> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/isVersionOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Entity> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/isVersionOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Entity> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/isVersionOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a specific versioned entity (dataset, software) to the entity it revises. Subproperty of prov:wasRevisionOf. Use together with rdip:version (data property) to form a complete version chain."@en .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/isVersionOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is version of"@en .
# 
