<https://w3id.org/rdip/usedDataset> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Records that a ResearchActivity consumed a given dcat:Dataset as input. Subproperty of prov:used."@en .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/usedDataset> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "used dataset"@en .
