<https://w3id.org/rdip/usedMethod> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/rdip/Method> .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/usedMethod> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a ResearchActivity to the formal Method or protocol it followed."@en .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/usedMethod> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "used method"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/rdip/usedSoftware
<https://w3id.org/rdip/usedSoftware> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
