<https://w3id.org/rdip/SoftwareApplication> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Software or computational tools used during research activities or produced as outputs. This includes scripts, libraries, ML frameworks, workflow engines and compiled programs. Version is captured via rdip:version; dependencies via rdip:softwareDependency; execution environment via rdip:ComputingEnvironment."@en .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/SoftwareApplication> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Research software"@en .
