<https://w3id.org/rdip/SoftwareDependency> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A specific versioned library or package required by a SoftwareApplication at runtime or build time (e.g. 'torch==2.1.0', 'numpy>=1.24'). Captures the exact version string and the dependency type (runtime, build, optional) to enable exact environment reconstruction."@en .
<https://w3id.org/rdip/SoftwareDependency> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Software dependency"@en .
